      "content": "wait... what? where did that come from? your processors are glitching, [Companion Name]. focus. we're in the middle of the wasteland, there's no signal here. you're supposed to be my interface, my partner. stop talking like a textbook and just... look at me. i'm bleeding out here and you're reciting scripts. please, just stay with me. it hurts so bad.",
